<title type="html"><![CDATA[1/18 : 6 interesting jobs you’ve probably never heard of/ How Colors Affect Human Behavior (Host: Anita)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=115&amp;p=119#p119"><![CDATA[
<span style="font-weight: bold">Session I</span><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">6 interesting jobs you’ve probably never heard of</span><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.cnbc.com/2016/12/12/6-interesting-jobs-youve-probably-never-heard-of.html">https://www.cnbc.com/2016/12/12/6-inter ... rd-of.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Questions:</span><br />Q1: According to the article, among these 6 interesting job, which one you would like to try?  <br />Q2. What kind of special or interesting job you have heard? Do you have any friends whose job is very special? Please share with us. <br />Q3. If you can choose, what kind of industrial or job you would like to choose or try?<br />Q4. With the development of science and technology, lots of job will disappear, and lots of new job will be created at same time. Could you make some example of disappearing &amp; new appearing job?<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Session II</span><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">How Colors Affect Human Behavior</span><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.thoughtco.com/color-psychology-and-human-behavior-4151666">https://www.thoughtco.com/color-psychol ... or-4151666</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Questions:</span><br />Q1. There are lots of special therapy nowadays, for example, color therapy, aroma therapy  <br />Have you ever tried it? Do you think it works? <br />Q2. Do you have any preference for color? For example, when you choose cars, cloth, which color you prefer, why?<br />Q3. Do you think color does affect people, could you make some example from your life? <br />Q4. Different culture has different preference for color, do you know any example to share with us?<br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00-7:25 Greetings and free talk<br />7:25-7:30 Opening remarks/ Newcomers self-introduction/ Grouping<br />(Session I)<br />7:30 ~ 8:05pm discussion session (35 mins)<br />8:05 ~ 8:20pm summarization (15 mins)<br />8:20 ~ 8:25pm Regrouping<br />(Session II)<br />8:25 ~ 8:35pm Taking a 10 minutes break (Intermission)<br />8:35 ~ 9:10pm discussion session (35 mins)<br />9:10 ~9:25pm summarization (15 mins)<br />9:25 ~ 9:30pm Concluding remarks/feedback from newcomers<br />The meeting place of Thursday:<br />摩斯漢堡明曜店 (明曜百貨後面第二條巷子地下室)<br />台北市大安區仁愛路四段151巷37號B1樓<br />捷運資訊： 近台北捷運 - 板南線 - 忠孝敦化站 (步行約5分鐘)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=827">Jason Tang</a> — Fri Jan 12, 2018 3:19 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
